{"tid":1044986,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【大白兔糖雪糕】洛杉磯瘋搶！ 生產商剝晒米紙遭鬧爆","createTime":"2019-03-03T09:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T13:11:49.000Z","uid":47272,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"18c40d51e04496122818264324e61a1869c8d10c","tid":1044986,"uid":47272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190303&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59324389\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190303%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59324389&d=96kHarChHvhp0Q8MKJCyECDm%2BQAENn3DIwfZikXBReQ%3D&h=9dee8903\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190303%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59324389&h=3157e268\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190303&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59324389</a><br />\n（新增動新聞）提到大白兔糖還停留在奶糖味潤唇膏，未免太過時了。美國洛杉磯有商家用大白兔糖作為原料，近日推出大白兔糖雪糕，推出市面就成為美國熱銷產品，迅速被搶光。不過，擁有大白兔商標的上海冠生園市場部負責人回應，這款雪糕並不是由冠生園授權在美國銷售生產的產品，也未與相關方面展開過合作。目前，冠生園正在通過第三方商標代理機構查詢，研究是否存在侵權行為。<br />\n<br />\n美國雪糕店Wanderlust Creamery推出的大白兔糖雪糕，一球就有1.3粒奶糖，起初宣傳只限量供應9天，但需求太大，決定將供應期延長至3個月。據生產商稱，目前最大困難是原材料大白兔糖都被搶光了。<br />\n這間雪糕店還在twitter「貼心」寫道：「我們已經幫你把煩人的米紙剝掉了。」網民不滿米紙被剝掉，想買下剝下來的所有米紙：「甚麼？米紙可是我最喜歡的！」「我無法信任一個說米紙『煩人』的生產商。」「天啊 ！我希望冰淇淋（雪糕）外面裹上米紙。」「我可以買下你剝下來的所有米紙嗎？」<br />\n<br />\ntwitter/北京時間<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/a5bv20kf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa5bv20kf&h=38e56e12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0u6darg3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0u6darg3&h=67c107a6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"259d40251590686cd765a77210954e8ba941a2c9","tid":1044986,"uid":50658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"中國人話人侵權<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438cee5440a34775d7ebbfec3d693208c064bde9","tid":1044986,"uid":239954,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T09:51:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d11cf4731d58f95256063bf2858f2ce54b159da","tid":1044986,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"果層衣點剝？"},{"pid":"c76d3d03f3becaf24865185876dc0810e1e05513","tid":1044986,"uid":115579,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:09:10.000Z","msg":"等睇港女又瘋搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c39398ab7656f93f652ce6c3a3a5eb3804df458c","tid":1044986,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d11cf4731d58f95256063bf2858f2ce54b159da","tid":1044986,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:07:16.000Z","msg":"果層衣點剝？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"浸水溶左佢先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}